{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.1","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:1","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.015.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les amis et les ennemis de David<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-4: cf. 2 S 19:24-30.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsque David eut un peu d\u00e9pass\u00e9 le sommet, voici, Tsiba, serviteur de Mephiboscheth, vint au-devant de lui avec deux \u00e2nes b\u00e2t\u00e9s, sur lesquels il y avait deux cents pains, cent masses de raisins secs, cent de fruits d\u2019\u00e9t\u00e9, et une outre de vin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.2","name":"2 Samuel 16:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.15.37","name":"2 Samuel 15:37","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.15.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.2","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:2","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Tsiba: Que veux-tu faire de cela? Et Tsiba r\u00e9pondit: Les \u00e2nes serviront de monture \u00e0 la maison du roi, le pain et les fruits d\u2019\u00e9t\u00e9 sont pour nourrir les jeunes gens, et le vin pour d\u00e9salt\u00e9rer ceux qui seront fatigu\u00e9s dans le d\u00e9sert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.3","name":"2 Samuel 16:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.1","name":"2 Samuel 16:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.3","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:3","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le roi dit: O\u00f9 est le fils de ton ma\u00eetre? Et Tsiba r\u00e9pondit au roi: Voici, il est rest\u00e9 \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, car il a dit: Aujourd\u2019hui la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl me rendra le royaume de mon p\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.4","name":"2 Samuel 16:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.2","name":"2 Samuel 16:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.4","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:4","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Le roi dit \u00e0 Tsiba: Voici, tout ce qui appartient \u00e0 Mephiboscheth est \u00e0 toi. Et Tsiba dit: Je me prosterne! Que je trouve gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 tes yeux, \u00f4 roi mon seigneur!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.5","name":"2 Samuel 16:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.3","name":"2 Samuel 16:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.5","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:5","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.006,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 5-14: cf. (2 S 19:16-23. 1 R 2:8, 9, 36-46.) Ps 7. 1 Pi 2:23.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>David \u00e9tait arriv\u00e9 jusqu\u2019\u00e0 Bachurim. Et voici, il sortit de l\u00e0 un homme de la famille et de la maison de Sa\u00fcl, nomm\u00e9 Schime\u00ef, fils de Gu\u00e9ra. Il s\u2019avan\u00e7a en pronon\u00e7ant des mal\u00e9dictions,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.6","name":"2 Samuel 16:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.4","name":"2 Samuel 16:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.6","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:6","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>et il jeta des pierres \u00e0 David et \u00e0 tous les serviteurs du roi David, tandis que tout le peuple et tous les hommes vaillants \u00e9taient \u00e0 la droite et \u00e0 la gauche du roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.7","name":"2 Samuel 16:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.5","name":"2 Samuel 16:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.7","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:7","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Schime\u00ef parlait ainsi en le maudissant: Va-t\u2019en, va-t\u2019en, homme de sang, m\u00e9chant homme!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.8","name":"2 Samuel 16:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.6","name":"2 Samuel 16:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.8","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:8","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel fait retomber sur toi tout le sang de la maison de Sa\u00fcl, dont tu occupais le tr\u00f4ne, et l\u2019\u00c9ternel a livr\u00e9 le royaume entre les mains d\u2019Absalom, ton fils; et te voil\u00e0 malheureux comme tu le m\u00e9rites, car tu es un homme de sang!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.9","name":"2 Samuel 16:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.7","name":"2 Samuel 16:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.9","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:9","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Alors Abischa\u00ef, fils de Tseruja, dit au roi: Pourquoi ce chien mort maudit-il le roi mon seigneur? Laisse-moi, je te prie, aller lui couper la t\u00eate.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.10","name":"2 Samuel 16:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.8","name":"2 Samuel 16:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.10","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:10","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Mais le roi dit: Qu\u2019ai-je affaire avec vous, fils de Tseruja? S\u2019il maudit, c\u2019est que l\u2019\u00c9ternel lui a dit: Maudis David! Qui donc lui dira: Pourquoi agis-tu ainsi?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.11","name":"2 Samuel 16:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.9","name":"2 Samuel 16:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.11","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:11","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et David dit \u00e0 Abischa\u00ef et \u00e0 tous ses serviteurs: Voici, mon fils, qui est sorti de mes entrailles, en veut \u00e0 ma vie; \u00e0 plus forte raison ce Benjamite! Laissez-le, et qu\u2019il maudisse, car l\u2019\u00c9ternel le lui a dit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.12","name":"2 Samuel 16:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.10","name":"2 Samuel 16:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.12","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:12","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Peut-\u00eatre l\u2019\u00c9ternel regardera-t-il mon affliction, et me fera-t-il du bien en retour des mal\u00e9dictions d\u2019aujourd\u2019hui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.13","name":"2 Samuel 16:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.11","name":"2 Samuel 16:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.13","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:13","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>David et ses gens continu\u00e8rent leur chemin. Et Schime\u00ef marchait sur le flanc de la montagne pr\u00e8s de David, et, en marchant, il maudissait, il jetait des pierres contre lui, il faisait voler la poussi\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.14","name":"2 Samuel 16:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.12","name":"2 Samuel 16:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.14","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:14","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Le roi et tout le peuple qui \u00e9tait avec lui arriv\u00e8rent \u00e0 Ajephim, et l\u00e0 ils se repos\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.15","name":"2 Samuel 16:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.13","name":"2 Samuel 16:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.15","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:15","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-19: cf. 2 S 15:32-37. (Ro 16:4. Ph 2:30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Absalom et tout le peuple, les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, \u00e9taient entr\u00e9s dans J\u00e9rusalem; et Achitophel \u00e9tait avec Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.16","name":"2 Samuel 16:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.14","name":"2 Samuel 16:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.16","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:16","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Lorsque Huscha\u00ef, l\u2019Arkien, ami de David, fut arriv\u00e9 aupr\u00e8s d\u2019Absalom, il lui dit: Vive le roi! Vive le roi!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.17","name":"2 Samuel 16:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.15","name":"2 Samuel 16:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.17","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:17","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et Absalom dit \u00e0 Huscha\u00ef: Voil\u00e0 donc l\u2019attachement que tu as pour ton ami! Pourquoi n\u2019es-tu pas all\u00e9 avec ton ami?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.18","name":"2 Samuel 16:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.16","name":"2 Samuel 16:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.18","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:18","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Huscha\u00ef r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 Absalom: C\u2019est que je veux \u00eatre \u00e0 celui qu\u2019ont choisi l\u2019\u00c9ternel et tout ce peuple et tous les hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et c\u2019est avec lui que je veux rester.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.19","name":"2 Samuel 16:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.17","name":"2 Samuel 16:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.19","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:19","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>D\u2019ailleurs, qui servirai-je? Ne sera-ce pas son fils? Comme j\u2019ai servi ton p\u00e8re, ainsi je te servirai.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.20","name":"2 Samuel 16:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.18","name":"2 Samuel 16:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.20","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:20","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-23: cf. 2 S 12:11, 12; 20:3.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Absalom dit \u00e0 Achitophel: Consultez ensemble; qu\u2019avons-nous \u00e0 faire?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.21","name":"2 Samuel 16:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.19","name":"2 Samuel 16:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.21","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:21","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et Achitophel dit \u00e0 Absalom: Va vers les concubines que ton p\u00e8re a laiss\u00e9es pour garder la maison; ainsi tout Isra\u00ebl saura que tu t\u2019es rendu odieux \u00e0 ton p\u00e8re, et les mains de tous ceux qui sont avec toi se fortifieront.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.22","name":"2 Samuel 16:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.20","name":"2 Samuel 16:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.22","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:22","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.016.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>On dressa pour Absalom une tente sur le toit, et Absalom alla vers les concubines de son p\u00e8re, aux yeux de tout Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.23","name":"2 Samuel 16:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.21","name":"2 Samuel 16:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.23","label":"","reference":"2 Samuel 16:23","prev_osis_id":"2Sam.016.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Sam.017.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Sam.16.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Les conseils donn\u00e9s en ce temps-l\u00e0 par Achitophel avaient autant d\u2019autorit\u00e9 que si l\u2019on e\u00fbt consult\u00e9 Dieu lui-m\u00eame. Il en \u00e9tait ainsi de tous les conseils d\u2019Achitophel, soit pour David, soit pour Absalom.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16","name":"2 Samuel 16","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.17.1","name":"2 Samuel 17:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.17.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Sam.16.22","name":"2 Samuel 16:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Sam.16.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb250de33.37250394');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb250de33.37250394\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb250de33.37250394","fum